ot free fall off of a granite cliff in Colorado cost \nhim a leg and almost his life, but did not stop him from pursuing his \npassion for the outdoors.In 2006 he became the first amputee to free \nclimb the nearly 10,000 ft. face of Yosemite's El Capitan in a single \nday. Now Craig hosts <em>Fight to Survive</em>, journeying to meet other \nsurvivors and hear their stories. Each week Craig takes a survivor back \nto the flashpoint of their ordeal as they share with him their very own \nfight to survive. This new series takes the audience right into to some \nof the most majestic and dangerous places in North America.</p><p>From the exciting action to the inspiring comebacks, these stories \nwill remind us all that faith, determination and human spirit can do \nanything when faced with the ultimate <em>Fight to Survive</em>.</p>","updated":1453817881,"_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/6960"},"previousepisode":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/401478"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/401463"}}},{"id":673097,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/673097/the-talk-2014-12-01-sherri-shepherd-big-boy","name":"Sherri Shepherd, Big Boy,","season":2014,"number":206,"airdate":"2014-12-01","airtime":"14:00","airstamp":"2014-12-01T14:00:00-05:00","runtime":60,"image":null,"summary":"","show":{"id":6049,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/6049/the-talk","name":"The Talk","type":"Talk Show","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Running","runtime":60,"premiered":"2011-09-27","schedule":{"time":"14:00","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":2,"name":"CBS","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"externals":{"tvrage":26645,"thetvdb":245071,"imdb":"tt1740718"},"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/41/103196.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/