isode":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1024391"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/57244"}}},{"id":57266,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/57266/crowd-control-1x03-travel-tricks","name":"Travel Tricks","season":1,"number":3,"airdate":"2014-12-01","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2014-12-01T21:00:00-05:00","runtime":30,"image":null,"summary":"<p>Examining ways to reduce stress during travel.</p>","show":{"id":600,"url":"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/600/crowd-control","name":"Crowd Control","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"Ended","runtime":30,"premiered":"2014-11-24","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":[]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":0,"network":{"id":42,"name":"National Geographic Channel","country":{"name":"United States","code":"US","timezone":"America/New_York"}},"webChannel":null,"externals":{"tvrage":46044,"thetvdb":287777,"imdb":"tt4153972"},"image":{"medium":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/4/12289.jpg","original":"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/4/12289.jpg"},"summary":"<p>In Crowd Control, viewers will discover that sometimes all you need is a little science to help make the world a better place. Best-selling author and behavior change expert Daniel Pink will use behavioral science to lead a series of experiments that show how we can apply the power of persuasion in our daily lives to reduce stress, minimize annoyances, improve health and increase happiness. Using hidden cameras to record his results, Pink will tackle the seemingly impossible task of righting everyday wrongs - from convincing partygoers to clean up their streets to stopping the senseless rush at an airport baggage claim.</p>","updated":1459192273,"_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/600"},"previousepisode":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/58243"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/57266"}}},{"id":99018,"url":"http://www.tvmaze